org.hkijena.jipipe.api.parameters

Class JIPipeParameterTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.parameters.JIPipeParameterTree
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeCustomParameterCollection, JIPipeParameterCollection

    public class JIPipeParameterTree
extends Object
implements JIPipeParameterCollection, JIPipeCustomParameterCollection
    An JIPipeParameterCollection that contains all the parameters of one or multiple JIPipeParameterCollection instances in a traversed form.
